how you're doing, you know. You nervous?

01:16:01.686 --> 01:16:04.689
Mary, you know,
I've done this a zillion times.

01:16:04.773 --> 01:16:08.151
I'm never nervous. Hand to God, not once.

01:16:08.276 --> 01:16:09.444
