01:18:02.182 --> 01:18:03.308
<i>Thank you three times.</i>

01:18:04.601 --> 01:18:06.895
<i>My granddaughter, ladies and gentlemen.</i>

01:18:12.192 --> 01:18:13.943
<i>Okay.</i>

