- Baby Doll!</i>

01:18:30.210 --> 01:18:31.878
Come on, Danny, play <i>Baby Doll!</i>

01:18:31.961 --> 01:18:34.547
- Yeah, Baby Doll!
- Whoo!

01:18:34.631 --> 01:18:36.800
Play <i>Baby Doll,</i> Danny!

01:18:36.883 --> 01:18:37.884
Whoo!

01:18:38.677 --> 01:18:41.388
- Play <i>Baby Doll!
- Baby Doll!</i>

01:18:41.471 --> 01:18:42.597
<i>Baby Doll,</i> Danny!

01:18:42.681 --> 01:18:44.724
<i>Baby Doll!</i>

01:18:44.808 --> 01:18:47.143
- Play <i>Baby Doll,</i> Danny!
<i>- Baby Doll!</i>

01:18:47.227 --> 01:18:50.313
- Play <i>Baby Doll,</i> Danny!
- Play <i>Baby Doll!</i>

01:19:05.412 --> 01:19:06.538
Phil.

01:19:07.789 --> 01:19:09.541
Can you just...

01:19:12.210 --> 01:19:14.295
<i>- Hello, everybody.
- Hi, Danny.</i>

01:19:14.379 --> 01:19:17.340
<i>Just working out a little something.</i>

01:19:17.674 --> 01:19:18.675
<i>Uh...</i>

01:19:18.925 --> 01:19:21.803
<i>But I know what you're here for.</i>

01:19:24.347 --> 01:19:25.682
<i>I think you know this one.</i>

01:19:29.644 --> 01:19:31.896
<i>Hey, baby doll</i>

01:19:31.980 --> 01:19:33.481
<i>What's going on?</i>

01:20:32.707 --> 01:20:34.250
Danny!

01:20:35.210 --> 01:20:36.211
Sophie!

01:20:37.420 --> 01:20:39.964
- Danny Collins.
- What are you doing here?

01:20:40.131 --> 01:20:43.051
Well, we heard about the gig and we're like,
"Let's go support our sugar daddy."

01:20:43.134 --> 01:20:44.302
Oh, yeah...

01:20:44.386 --> 01:20:47.681
