I hope that's okay.

01:20:47.764 --> 01:20:49.516
What's up? What do you got on you?

01:20:49.599 --> 01:20:50.600
What do you mean?

01:20:50.684 --> 01:20:52.227
Come on. Come on. What do I mean?

01:20:52.310 --> 01:20:53.436
Come on, babe, he wants to party.

01:20:53.520 --> 01:20:54.521
