01:20:54.604 --> 01:20:58.149
- I got it all, baby. I got it all.
- Okay.

01:21:01.528 --> 01:21:02.570
Mmm.

01:21:02.612 --> 01:21:04.197
Yeah.
Uh-huh.

01:21:08.868 --> 01:21:10.787
Here you go, Danny.

01:21:10.870 --> 01:21:12.831
- Oh, man.
- Yeah.

01:21:12.914 --> 01:21:14.499
It's good.

01:21:21.256 --> 01:21:23.508
I fired the pool guy and the gardener.

01:21:23.591 --> 01:21:26.219
I really didn't like the
way he looked at me.

01:21:26.302 --> 01:21:27.622
You know, I decided to start...

01:21:27.637 --> 01:21:29.014
