01:39:48.822 --> 01:39:54.536
Literally, every time, it's a good thing
when he calls you Tom.

01:39:55.078 --> 01:39:59.416
So this is what we want right now.

01:40:00.417 --> 01:40:05.422
We want him to come in here,
open that door, call you Tom.

01:40:07.924 --> 01:40:09.592
That's what we want.

01:40:10.260 --> 01:40:12.012
You understand?

01:40:12.095 --> 01:40:14.597
So let's... Let's focus...

